Added a Unix installer at `sdks/browser4-cli/install.sh` and documented it in `sdks/browser4-cli/README.md` and the root `README.md`.

The installer now:
- detects supported package managers
- installs missing Java 17+, Google Chrome, Rust, and native build deps
- downloads the latest released `Browser4.jar` into `~/.browser4/lib`
- installs `browser4-cli` from the latest tagged Browser4 source into `~/.local/bin`
- supports `BROWSER4_INSTALL_VERSION`, `BROWSER4_INSTALL_ROOT`, and `BROWSER4_LIB_DIR` overrides

